  (17975, 23, 15, 6, 'For the waters of Nimrim shall be desolate: for the hay is withered away, the grass faileth, there is no green thing.', '&para; 2~04325~ 4~05249~ 7~04923~: 10~02682~ 13~03001~, 15~01877~ 16~03615~, 21~03418~.'),
