  (31110, 66, 22, 14, 'Blessed are they that do his commandments, that they may have right to the tree of life, and may enter in through the gates into the city.', '0~3107~ [1] 4~4160~ 5~846~ 6~1785~, 7~2443~ 8~846~ 10~2071~ 11~1849~ 12~1909~ 14~3586~ 16~2222~, 17~2532~ 19~1525~ 23~4440~ 24~1519~ 26~4172~.'),
  (22852, 37, 1, 3, 'Then came the word of the LORD by Haggai the prophet, saying,', '3~01697~ 6~03068~ 7~03027~ 8~02292~ 10~05030~, 11~0559~,'),
