  (7341, 9, 6, 3, 'And they said, If ye send away the ark of the God of Israel, send it not empty; but in any wise return him a trespass offering: then ye shall be healed, and it shall be known to you why his hand is not removed from you.', '2~0559~, 6~07971~ 8~0727~ 11~0430~ 13~03478~, 14~07971~ 17~07387~; 21~07725~ 22~07725~ 26~0817~: 31~07495~, 36~03045~ 41~03027~ 44~05493~'),
