  (15942, 19, 119, 35, 'Make me to go in the path of thy commandments; for therein do I delight.', '&para; 3~01869~ 6~05410~ 9~04687~; 14~02654~.'),
  (3787, 4, 4, 39, 'From thirty years old and upward even unto fifty years old, every one that entereth into the service, for the work in the tabernacle of the congregation,', '1~07970~ 2~08141~ 3~01121~ 5~04605~ 8~02572~ 9~08141~ 10~01121~, 14~0935~ 17~06635~, 20~05656~ 23~0168~ 26~04150~,'),
  (11424, 14, 11, 1, 'And when Rehoboam was come to Jerusalem, he gathered of the house of Judah and Benjamin an hundred and fourscore thousand chosen men, which were warriors, to fight against Israel, that he might bring the kingdom again to Rehoboam.', '&para; 2~07346~ 4~0935~ 6~03389~, 8~06950~ 11~01004~ 13~03063~ 15~01144~ 17~03967~ 19~08084~ 20~0505~ 21~0977~ [22] 25~06213~ 26~04421~,* 28~03898~ 30~03478~, 34~07725~ 36~04467~ 37~07725~ 39~07346~.'),
  (30944, 66, 14, 2, 'And I heard a voice from heaven, as the voice of many waters, and as the voice of a great thunder: and I heard the voice of harpers harping with their harps:', '0~2532~ 2~191~ 4~5456~ 5~1537~ 6~3772~, 7~5613~ 9~5456~ 11~4183~ 12~5204~, 13~2532~ 14~5613~ 16~5456~ 19~3173~ 20~1027~: 21~2532~ 23~191~ 25~5456~ 27~2790~ 28~2789~ 29~1722~ 30~846~ 31~2788~:'),
  (31115, 66, 22, 19, 'And if any man shall take away from the words of the book of this prophecy, God shall take away his part out of the book of life, and out of the holy city, and from the things which are written in this book.', '0~2532~ 1~1437~ 3~5100~ 6~851~ 7~575~ 9~3056~ 12~976~ 14~5129~ 15~4394~, 16~2316~ 19~851~ 20~846~ 21~3313~ 23~575~ 25~976~ 27~2222~, 28~2532~ 30~1537~ 32~40~ 33~4172~, 34~2532~ [35] 40~1125~ 41~1722~ 42~5026~ 43~975~.'),
