  (11648, 14, 21, 15, 'And thou shalt have great sickness by disease of thy bowels, until thy bowels fall out by reason of the sickness day by day.', '[2 3] 4~07227~ 5~02483~ 7~04245~ 10~04578~, 13~04578~ 15~03318~ 20~02483~ 21~03117~ 23~03117~.'),
  (19843, 24, 35, 11, 'But it came to pass, when Nebuchadrezzar king of Babylon came up into the land, that we said, Come, and let us go to Jerusalem for fear of the army of the Chaldeans, and for fear of the army of the Syrians: so we dwell at Jerusalem.', '6~05019~ 7~04428~ 9~0894~ 11~05927~ 14~0776~, 17~0559~, 18~0935~, 22~0935~ 24~03389~ 26~06440~ 29~02428~ 32~03778~, 35~06440~ 38~02428~ 41~0758~: 44~03427~ 46~03389~.'),
