  (24704, 41, 12, 20, 'Now there were seven brethren: and the first took a wife, and dying left no seed.', '2~2258~ 3~2033~ 4~80~: 5~2532~ 7~4413~ 8~2983~ 10~1135~, 11~2532~ 12~599~ 13~863~ 14~3756~ 15~4690~.'),
