  (26576, 43, 11, 38, 'Jesus therefore again groaning in himself cometh to the grave. It was a cave, and a stone lay upon it.', '0~2424~ 1~3767~ 2~3825~ 3~1690~ 4~1722~ 5~1438~ 6~2064~ 7~1519~ 9~3419~ 10~1161~.* 12~2258~ 14~4693~, 15~2532~ 17~3037~ 18~1945~ 19~1909~ 20~846~.'),
