  (19806, 24, 33, 22, 'As the host of heaven cannot be numbered, neither the sand of the sea measured: so will I multiply the seed of David my servant, and the Levites that minister unto me.', '2~06635~ 4~08064~ 7~05608~, 10~02344~ 13~03220~ 14~04058~: 18~07235~ 20~02233~ 22~01732~ 24~05650~, 27~03881~ 29~08334~'),
