  (30859, 66, 9, 3, 'And there came out of the smoke locusts upon the earth: and unto them was given power, as the scorpions of the earth have power.', '0~2532~ 2~1831~ 4~1537~ 6~2586~ 7~200~ 8~1519~ 10~1093~: 11~2532~ 13~846~ 15~1325~ 16~1849~, 17~5613~ 19~4651~ 22~1093~ 23~2192~ 24~1849~.'),
