  (4056, 4, 11, 27, 'And there ran a young man, and told Moses, and said, Eldad and Medad do prophesy in the camp.', '2~07323~ 5~05288~, 7~05046~ 8~04872~, 10~0559~, 11~0419~ 13~04312~ 15~05012~ 18~04264~.'),
