  (1791, 2, 10, 9, 'And Moses said, We will go with our young and with our old, with our sons and with our daughters, with our flocks and with our herds will we go; for we must hold a feast unto the LORD.', '1~04872~ 2~0559~, 5~03212~ 8~05288~ 12~02205~, 15~01121~ 19~01323~, 22~06629~ 26~01241~ 29~03212~; [32 33] 35~02282~ 38~03068~.'),
