  (18928, 23, 65, 22, 'They shall not build, and another inhabit; they shall not plant, and another eat: for as the days of a tree are the days of my people, and mine elect shall long enjoy the work of their hands.', '3~01129~, 5~0312~ 6~03427~; 10~05193~, 12~0312~ 13~0398~: 17~03117~ 20~06086~ [21] 23~03117~ 26~05971~, 29~0972~ 32~01086~ 34~04639~ 37~03027~.'),
