  (329, 1, 13, 7, 'And there was a strife between the herdmen of Abram''s cattle and the herdmen of Lot''s cattle: and the Canaanite and the Perizzite dwelled then in the land.', '4~07379~ 7~07462~ 9~087~ 10~04735~ 13~07462~ 15~03876~ 16~04735~: 19~03669~ 22~06522~ 23~03427~ 27~0776~.'),
  (5185, 5, 9, 22, 'And at Taberah, and at Massah, and at Kibrothhattaavah, ye provoked the LORD to wrath.', '2~08404~, 5~04532~, 8~06914~, 12~03068~ 14~07107~.'),
