  (23032, 38, 10, 7, 'And they of Ephraim shall be like a mighty man, and their heart shall rejoice as through wine: yea, their children shall see it, and be glad; their heart shall rejoice in the LORD.', '[1 2] 3~0669~ 8~01368~ [9] 12~03820~ 14~08055~ 17~03196~: 20~01121~ 22~07200~ [23] 26~08055~; 28~03820~ 30~01523~ 33~03068~.'),
