  (30987, 66, 16, 17, 'And the seventh angel poured out his vial into the air; and there came a great voice out of the temple of heaven, from the throne, saying, It is done.', '&para; 0~2532~ 2~1442~ 3~32~ 5~1632~ 6~846~ 7~5357~ 8~1519~ 10~109~; 11~2532~ 13~1831~ 15~3173~ 16~5456~ 18~575~ 20~3485~ 22~3772~, 23~575~ 25~2362~, 26~3004~, 29~1096~.'),
