  (9790, 12, 9, 26, 'Surely I have seen yesterday the blood of Naboth, and the blood of his sons, saith the LORD; and I will requite thee in this plat, saith the LORD. Now therefore take and cast him into the plat of ground, according to the word of the LORD.', '3~07200~ 4~0570~ 6~01818~ 8~05022~, 11~01818~ 14~01121~, 15~05002~ 17~03068~; 21~07999~ 25~02513~, 26~05002~ 28~03068~. 31~05375~ [32] 33~07993~ 37~02513~ [38 39] 43~01697~ 46~03068~.'),
