  (8313, 10, 12, 20, 'Then David arose from the earth, and washed, and anointed himself, and changed his apparel, and came into the house of the LORD, and worshipped: then he came to his own house; and when he required, they set bread before him, and he did eat.', '1~01732~ 2~06965~ 5~0776~, 7~07364~, 9~05480~ [10] 12~02498~ 14~08071~, 16~0935~ 19~01004~ 22~03068~, 24~07812~: 27~0935~ 31~01004~; 35~07592~, 37~07760~ 38~03899~ 44~0398~.'),
