  (19371, 24, 17, 5, 'Thus saith the LORD; Cursed be the man that trusteth in man, and maketh flesh his arm, and whose heart departeth from the LORD.', '&para; 1~0559~ 3~03068~; 4~0779~ [5] 7~01397~ 9~0982~ 11~0120~, 13~07760~ 14~01320~ 16~02220~, 19~03820~ 20~05493~ 23~03068~.'),
