  (28114, 45, 7, 7, 'What shall we say then? is the law sin? God forbid. Nay, I had not known sin, but by the law: for I had not known lust, except the law had said, Thou shalt not covet.', '&para; 0~5101~ 3~2046~ 4~3767~? [5] 7~3551~ 8~266~? 10~1096~ 11~3361~.* 12~235~, 14~1097~ 15~3756~ 16~1097~ 17~266~, 18~1508~ 19~1223~ 21~3551~: 22~5037~ 23~1063~ 24~1492~ 25~3756~ 26~1492~ 27~1939~, 28~1508~ 30~3551~ 32~3004~, 34~1937~ 35~3756~ 36~1937~.'),
