  (25098, 42, 4, 23, 'And he said unto them, Ye will surely say unto me this proverb, Physician, heal thyself: whatsoever we have heard done in Capernaum, do also here in thy country.', '0~2532~ 2~2036~ 3~4314~ 4~846~, 6~2046~ 7~3843~ 8~2046~ 10~3427~ 11~5026~ 12~3850~, 13~2395~, 14~2323~ 15~4572~: 16~3745~ 19~191~ 20~1096~ 21~1722~ 22~2584~, 23~4160~ 24~2532~ 25~5602~ 26~1722~ 27~4675~ 28~3968~.'),
